539
00:34:51,196 --> 00:34:52,863
te vijne ne Sahaja Yoga,

540
00:34:53,196 --> 00:34:55,488
s'eshte e thene te vijne ne Sahaja Yoga.

541
00:34:55,863 --> 00:34:57,405
Pra, ju jeni kaq fatlume

542
00:34:57,779 --> 00:35:01,654
