545
00:35:10,363 --> 00:35:13,405
Dhe me kete ju do te dini sa te cmuar

546
00:35:13,779 --> 00:35:16,572
jeni ju per kete bote,

547
00:35:16,946 --> 00:35:19,071
dhe ajo qe ju duhet te beni s'eshte

548
00:35:19,405 --> 00:35:22,155
te mendoni per fitimin material, fizik

549
00:35:22,612 --> 00:35:27,863
apo fitime emocionale, por fitime shpirterore.

550
00:35:28,738 --> 00:35:33,280
