597
00:38:23,447 --> 00:38:26,196
Ai tha, "Ne rregull." Ai vetem u perul dhe u lut,

598
00:38:26,530 --> 00:38:28,696
"Nene, te lutem sheroje xhaxhain tim."

599
00:38:29,113 --> 00:38:30,572
